          <h1>Create account</h1>
<p class="auth-subtitle">
  Already have an account? <a href="login.html">Sign in</a>
</p>
<p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--warm-grey);background:var(--off-white);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:10px 14px;margin-bottom:8px;">
  This signup is for <strong style="color:var(--navy)">clients only</strong>. Staff and admin accounts are created by the AmyServes team.
